In memory of
Pamela McGranaghan
A garden of beautiful memories
Sprayed with a million tears
1937-2019

Nan
Arms that always reached out
To hug and hold
Love that was never ending,
A heat that was made of gold
Nan,
We miss you

IN LOVING MEMORY OF
PAMELA LOIS AVRIL
McGRANAGHAN
1937-2019
SADLY MISSED"á
